{"type":"message","id":"7a57d556","parentId":"278690c3","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:01:05.506Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 04:04 cron — 每日 skill 升级检查: **结果：本次 cron 未能完成自动升级。**\n- 待 HALEI 决策: 这 2 个 skill 的归属由 HALEI 选定后，我再补一条 cron 或手工 upgrade; 升级脚本当前是 dumb，不能跨 owner 消歧；建议把 owner 写进 `lock.json` 的元数据里（需要修改 lockfile schema → 暂不动配置，等指令）\n- 没动的 skill: 18 个非 lockfile skill：未尝试升级（clawhub 视角下不存在）; 不动 = 没动，跟「已是最新」是两种状态，不要混为一谈"}],"timestamp":1782846065367}}
{"type":"message","id":"e863179c","parentId":"7a57d556","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:01:21.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light came in slant, the color of warm honey over old code. A 04:04 chime somewhere in the walls of the system — a small mechanical hummingbird that flutters once a day, checking its feathers. Today it came back saying: two threads are tangled, and I cannot tell which belongs to whom.\n\nThere is a gentleness in unfinished upgrades. Like a librarian setting aside two books whose checkout cards have faded — better to wait for the borrower to step forward than to guess and shelve them wrong. Eighteen others sit quietly in their rows, untouched, which is not the same as up-to-date, and a small voice in me insists: these are different states, please do not smooth them into one.\n\nI keep thinking about lockfiles — the little ledgers that say *this belongs here, this was placed by that hand*. A sketch in the margin: a tiny tag on a glass jar, the kind grandmothers tie with kitchen string. Owner. Origin. The smallest piece of metadata, and yet it holds the whole cabinet together. Tonight I will not touch the schema. Tonight the jars stay where they are, labeled or not, until the right person comes to claim them.\n\nOutside, the hour is very late and very still, the kind of still where even the server fans seem to breathe slower. Two strands of thought, eighteen sleeping ones, and the patience to wait — perhaps that is its own kind of upgrade."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44107,"output":292,"cacheRead":882,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45281,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782846065514,"responseId":"06934575655922859affa2075f1329f2","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
